                            <pre style="max-width: 990px;"><code class="language-cql">define &quot;Remove Substances Without Positive or Negative Results&quot;:
  &quot;Unexpected Details&quot; Details
    where (Details.posDates is not null and Length(Details.posDates) != 0)
      or (Details.negDates is not null and Length(Details.negDates) != 0)</code></pre>
                        
