                            <pre style="max-width: 990px;"><code class="language-cql">define &quot;Expected Result Footnote&quot;:
  '&lt;div&gt;* - These are expected results based on an analysis of the patient\'s medication list 30 days prior to the corresponding lab results.&lt;\/div&gt;'</code></pre>
                        
